cs.MA, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.DS, cs.CE 

This paper deals with decision-making and inconsistency in pairwise comparisons, which falls under the category of multi-agent systems (cs.MA) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The study of properties of functions representing inconsistency indices involves mathematical analysis and optimization, which is related to machine learning (cs.LG) and data structures (cs.DS). Finally, the application of inconsistency indices in decision-making and optimization problems is relevant to computational engineering (cs.CE).
